MSG_SHORT_KICKABORT
\ebBrcni\en bo odklopil izbranega uporabnika\nin prekinil vse prenose, ki jih ima.\n\ebPrekini\en prekine le njegove prenose.
; \ebKick\en will disconnect the selected\nuser and any transfers they are doing\n\ebAbort\en will just cancel their transfer
;
