MSG_CONTROL_CODES
Uporabljate lahko naslednje nadzorne kode:\n$u = trenutni uporabniki\n$m = najv. uporabnikov\n$c = najv. prenos/s\n$s = najv. prenos / trenutni uporabniki
; You can use the following control codes:\n$u = Current users\n$m = Max users\n$c = Max CPS\n$s = MaxCPS/Current users
;
MSG_UPLOAD
%s [%s]\n%s\n%s\n%s (%lu/%lu bajtov, %lu znakov/s)
; %s [%s]\n%s\n%s\n%s (%lu/%lu bytes, %lu cps)
;
